node.text: of many skincare videos?? We'll see 😘 #teamipartner  I've never really raved about skincare before.. I'm not a guru but I wanted to share with you guys! I have pretty sensitive skin, I get most of my breakouts on my chin and cheeks, especially from my makeup. The biggest thing I love about this detox mask from @teamiblends that I can literally feel it pulling everything out but isn't stripping like others that I've used. It's the only mask I use now and it's gentle so using it 3x a week is fine! It's literally perfect for me and has my skin glowing 😍 At only $20 you definitely need it in your routine! Use SAM30 for 30% off. #thankyouteami

node.text: I just want to say thank you to everyone that came out yesterday for the Grand Opening of @sweetheartcoast ! I can’t thank you enough for supporting me!! It was so fun seeing and meeting you all ☺️☺️ you all rock! Special thank you to the town of Ocean City NJ, @oceancityvacation especially the police & surrounding stores on the boardwalk! If you are ever visiting please support all Ocean City local businesses! It’s official, let the Summer begin.. come shop away @sweetheartcoast IS NOW OPEN!! 🤍🤍🤍
